Documentation of XviD
-----------------------

xvid-decoding.txt
=================
A short overview of routine(s) and data structures needed for 
decoding with XviD-API.



xvid-encoder.txt
================
A short overview of routine(s) and data structure needed for
encoding with XviD-API.


Questions and suggestions to the forums at http://www.xvid.org
